name: Just Did it
description:
"Just Did It, Nike", 2021, digital collage of watercolor painting and digital elements - pixel filter

My work is a mixture of impatience and sensitivity to the world in which I live. I'm super influenced by the pop and urban culture - the "cool kid" attitude fascinates me. We're surrounded by brands and their slogans. How does it influence us? We're ready to purchase 200$ worth Nike shoes so we can show our Instagram followers how cool we are. Is it really cool though?
